      <title>高盛的斯尼德表示正等待中国推出刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/goldman-s-sneader-says-in-waiting-mode-for-china-stimulus-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团亚太区（日本除外）总裁凯文·斯尼德 (Kevin Sneader) 表示，在去年下半年看到一些发展势头之后，高盛集团和客户正在观望中国政府是否会推出重大刺激措施来重振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/goldman-s-sneader-says-in-waiting-mode-for-china-stimulus-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:55:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国进口创纪录推动铁矿石需求上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/iron-ore-advances-after-record-china-imports-boost-demand-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示，中国年度炼钢原料进口量达到创纪录水平，且贸易顺差大幅增加，此后铁矿石价格再次飙升至每吨 100 美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/iron-ore-advances-after-record-china-imports-boost-demand-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税报告导致美元走弱，铜价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/copper-extends-rally-as-dollar-weakens-on-trump-tariff-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，即将上任的特朗普政府将缓慢提高贸易关税，而不是一次性征收巨额关税，铜价延续了今年的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/copper-extends-rally-as-dollar-weakens-on-trump-tariff-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:27:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台币将取代人民币成为亚洲主要融资货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/taiwan-dollar-set-to-replace-yuan-as-asia-s-top-funding-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率和汇率波动风险较低，台币即将取代人民币成为亚洲最佳套利交易目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/taiwan-dollar-set-to-replace-yuan-as-asia-s-top-funding-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:22:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称阿波罗将考虑以 20 亿美元的估值在印度进行 Tenneco IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/apollo-is-said-to-consider-ipo-for-tenneco-s-indian-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 正考虑将汽车零部件供应商天纳克公司 (Tenneco Inc.) 的印度业务上市，加入其他已在全球人口最多的国家进行或计划首次公开募股 (IPO) 的公司之列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/apollo-is-said-to-consider-ipo-for-tenneco-s-indian-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制药公司召开大型会议 因医疗成本问题引发抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/pharma-s-big-meeting-in-us-draws-protests-over-healthcare-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，制药业最大的投资会议在旧金山吸引了大批抗议者，抗议者举着写有“拖延、否认、罢免”的标语。检察官称，这些标语是上个月在一名健康保险公司高管被杀现场发现的弹壳上写的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/pharma-s-big-meeting-in-us-draws-protests-over-healthcare-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:15:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶市政公用事业公司因帕利塞兹火灾缺水而被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/la-city-utility-sued-over-water-shortage-during-palisades-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶市电力和水务公司因未能提供足够的水来扑灭美国第二大都市目前最大的火灾而遭到诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/la-city-utility-sued-over-water-shortage-during-palisades-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 02:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球供应风险加剧，油价持于五个月高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁，以及即将上任的特朗普政府可能实施的贸易关税，对全球供应构成威胁，油价维持在五个月高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 23:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：关税报告推动美元下跌，中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有消息称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的经济团队成员讨论了逐步提高关税的方法，中国股市引领亚洲股市走高，而美元则走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克利夫兰克利夫斯和纽柯考虑联合竞购美国钢铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/cleveland-cliffs-and-nucor-said-to-consider-joint-us-steel-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司正与纽柯公司合作，考虑联合竞购美国钢铁公司。克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司的高层后来在新闻发布会上证实了他对这家美国钢铁制造商的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/cleveland-cliffs-and-nucor-said-to-consider-joint-us-steel-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
